      "para_id": "Q001860.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Nindara , the mighty master , his master , Ur-Ninĝirsu , ( also called ? ) En-me-zid-ana , the šennu priest , the beloved en priest of Nanše , fashioned this ( statuette ) for the well-being of Ibbi-Suen , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters ."
    }
